{"tid":706624,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一次世盃，就睇到多左幾多 小學雞/忽然球迷/賭仔","createTime":"2018-06-18T04:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T06:14:24.000Z","uid":72652,"like":32,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"499b6b1d3d49ed65b715355f63929de3f60ed8bd","tid":706624,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"足球一向都係踢11個人<br />\n一場波都打得好<br />\n要成隊波的配合<br />\n<br />\nD忽然球迷真係以為有球星就會贏緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有少少足球知識都知<br />\n打穩守突擊永遠易過控球主攻<br />\n今屆幾支強隊<br />\n德國 阿根廷 巴西 西班牙<br />\n都係比大巴陣屈死左<br />\n<br />\n咁足球戰術當然無分對錯<br />\n贏到就係好戰術<br />\n<br />\n但係班小學雞以為破大巴真係求其隊入去就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估打籃球鬥射三分咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d155524034e4bf6c59dcfc55ca5d9c9690e3c80e","tid":706624,"uid":155137,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:00:14.000Z","msg":"99%球員都做唔到 但係C7示範左"},{"pid":"f96b41273b60bd6c0060a5312b6abe7b2b21d701","tid":706624,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"係1+10"},{"pid":"3c15a70b49262234652ca1a8e2163140b3afea6b","tid":706624,"uid":72652,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d155524034e4bf6c59dcfc55ca5d9c9690e3c80e","tid":706624,"uid":155137,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:00:14.000Z","msg":"99%球員都做唔到 但係C7示範左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"西班牙係打控球主攻個邊喎"},{"pid":"6502bd9c4a73e7804956c44cf4e826a5612b6f4a","tid":706624,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:04:46.000Z","msg":"多左幾左?"},{"pid":"ae3fb020ff528d8f46a272ee6519730c8992125e","tid":706624,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":